strings.Value: "Well? Didn't I tell you that no one's so saintly? Tristian was definitely hiding something? Ring any bells? Ah, but you never listen, as usual..."
"If we listened to everything you said, our heads would burst."
"And how many of your predictions and premonitions in the same period were false?"
"Don't pout â€” you were right, you were, ha ha hmm. I never thought that snotnose could pull such a trick."
"I don't drink your wordy vomits, no! Too much of those!"
"I must admit, I didn't expect such a monstrous lie, even from him. I sensed there was a scorpion in the party, but I never suspected a giant manticore!"
